title: #072 - Growing a Successful Product-Based Business on Instagram with Jessica Williamson
itunes:title: #072 - Growing a Successful Product-Based Business on Instagram with Jessica Williamson
description: In our 72th episode, we welcome Jessica Williamson, Founder of Somewear Elsewhere and Founder/Managing Director of Ete Swimwear. Jessica shares how she was able to make 6 figures in her first 12 months of selling a physical product and what she invested in that got her invited to New York Fashion Week in her first week of launching. If you have a product-based business or need some advice on photo shoots, influencer marketing or email marketing, this is the episode for you!
